---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base
  title="Terms of Service — Praetor by Katafract"
  description="Praetor Terms of Service. Coming soon with Sovereign subscription."
  ogDescription="Praetor is in development. Terms of Service coming when the app enters TestFlight."
  section="prose"
>
  <link slot="head" rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css" />

  <div class="prose-header">
    <p class="prose-eyebrow">Praetor &mdash; Terms of Service</p>
    <h1>Praetor Terms of Service</h1>
    <p class="prose-meta">Katafract LLC &mdash; Coming with Sovereign &mdash; <a href="//terms">All app terms &rarr;</a></p>
  </div>

  <div class="prose-body">

    <div class="callout">
      <p>Praetor is in development. The full Terms of Service will be published when Praetor enters TestFlight. For now, know this: Praetor will be a native app included with your Sovereign subscription. You own your data. We don't store it, scan it, or sell it.</p>
    </div>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>If you have questions about Praetor's terms, reach out:</p>
    <div class="contact-card">
      <h3>Legal Inquiries</h3>
      <p>Katafract LLC</p>
      <p><a href="mailto:legal@katafract.com">legal@katafract.com</a></p>
      <p>We typically respond within one business day.</p>
    </div>

  </div>

</Base>
